<del rend="strikethrough">von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>kunigkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> gnaden </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_101_r3l24">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> </del> <expan>gnedikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>auſʒrıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab></add> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tigen</expan> wölle / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_101_line_1574776097832_566">Als etc </ab></add> Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_101" id="49r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Künig </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger fürst und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns ist fürbraht worden,
                        wie daz der hochgeporen fürste, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> tochterman,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von
                        Osterreich, etliche <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kauffleute mitsampt
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> habe und kauffmanschaft in dem gepirge in
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>herschäft<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>gepiet<ex>en</ex></expan> aufgehalten und bekümert hab und
                        wir doch niht wissen, daz wir mit seinen <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ichts <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> czuschicken
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> lieb und gute. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>künigkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>tochterman<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                        durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinst <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        geruchet <expan>ernstlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und kauffleute mitsampt
                            <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> hab und kauffmanschaft on hindernüsse ledig
                        lasse. Und waz auch Hans <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> diener, <expan>weys<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dicz briefs, darümb an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add><expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan></add> bringe von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<add><expan>k<ex>üniklich</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan></add> darynne <add>gütlich</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> und <add>im</add> des
                                <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <add>in auch</add> darümb
                                    <add><expan>gnedikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>auszrichte<ex>n</ex></expan> und</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>tigen</expan> wölle, <add>als etc.</add> Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
